  <entry>
    <title>php 验证码</title>
    <url>/2020/11/04/php%E5%86%99%E7%9A%84%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>php练手随笔</p>
<h2 id="搭建验证码宽高">搭建验证码宽高</h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$width</span>=120;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$height</span>=40;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$img</span>=imagecreatetruecolor(<span class="variable">$width</span>,<span class="variable">$height</span>); //搭建验证码背景的宽高</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="给验证码分配颜色">给验证码分配颜色</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorbg</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(150,255),rand(150,255),rand(150,255));//給验证码随机分配三原色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorBorder</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(200,255),rand(200,255),rand(200,255));//边框随机分配三原色 这部可以不需要只是添加函数用的</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorString</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(10,100),rand(10,100),rand(10,100));//线条随机分配三原色</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="创建验证码">创建验证码</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">imagefill(<span class="variable">$img</span>,0,0,<span class="variable">$colorbg</span>);//创建验证码 参数风别是验证码，从x轴开始，从y轴开始，背景颜色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">imagerectangle(<span class="variable">$img</span>,0,0,<span class="variable">$width</span>-1,<span class="variable">$height</span>-1,<span class="variable">$colorBorder</span>);//创建边框 参数分别是验证码，从左x轴开始，从左y轴开始，从左x轴结束，从左y轴结束，背景颜色</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="这样一个验证码的框架就搭建好了不过是没有随机数么有线条也没有那些点点点的随机数">这样一个验证码的框架就搭建好了不过是没有随机数么有线条也没有那些点点点的随机数</h3>
<h3 id="接下来美化下验证码">接下来美化下验证码</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;100;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	imagesetpixel(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(0,<span class="variable">$width</span>-1),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>-1),imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(100,200),rand(100,200),rand(100,200)));//imagesetpixel是分配点，imagecolorallocate是点的颜色</span><br><span class="line">&#125;//循环給验证码添加小点,个人感觉这部完全没必要</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;5;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	imageline(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(0,<span class="variable">$width</span>/2),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>),rand(<span class="variable">$width</span>/2,<span class="variable">$width</span>),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>),imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(100,200),rand(100,200),rand(100,200)));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;//循环給验证码画线  //创建边框 参数分别是验证码，从左x轴开始到中间结束，从左y轴开始到中间结束，从中间x轴到右边x轴结束，从中间y轴到右边y轴结束，背景颜色  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="给验证码创建随机数">给验证码创建随机数</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$element</span>=array(<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;d&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;e&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;f&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;g&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;h&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;i&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;j&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;k&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;m&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;p&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;q&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;s&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;t&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;v&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;y&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;z&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$string</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;//创建个空数组</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;4;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable">$string</span>.=<span class="variable">$element</span>[rand(0,count(<span class="variable">$element</span>)-1)];//随机从数组取值到空数组里</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//ucwords(strtoupper(<span class="variable">$string</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>));//原本是想将string的内容强制装换成大写的，但是无法转换.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>我注释的这步想将内容全部转换成大写的但是搞不明白为什么空数组会先进行转换或者就是报错</p>
<h3 id="给验证码添加随机数">给验证码添加随机数</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">imagettftext(<span class="variable">$img</span>,28,rand(-5,5),rand(15,20),rand(30,35),<span class="variable">$colorString</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;c:\WINDOWS\Fonts\STCAIYUN.TTF&#x27;</span>,<span class="variable">$string</span>);;//用Truetpye写入文本////imagestring(<span class="variable">$img</span>,5,0,0,<span class="string">&#x27;abcd&#x27;</span>,<span class="variable">$colorString</span>);//水平写入内容</span><br><span class="line">//imagettftext参数风别是验证码，字体大小，字体偏移角度，从x轴开始，从y轴开始，字体颜色,使用的字体路径，显示内容,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="然后对浏览器进行声明">然后对浏览器进行声明</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">imagejpeg(<span class="variable">$img</span>);//告诉浏览器这是图片，头部一定要加header(<span class="string">&quot;Content-type:image/jpeg&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">imagedestroy(<span class="variable">$img</span>);//销毁图像回收资源不然会越运行越卡</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="记得一定要在第一行加上这句话">记得一定要在第一行加上这句话</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php header(<span class="string">&quot;Content-type:image/jpeg;charset=utf-8&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这步的目的是告诉浏览器这是图片不是代码，没有这部的话可能会读取成乱码</p>
<h3 id="全部代码">全部代码</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php header(<span class="string">&quot;Content-type:image/jpeg;charset=utf-8&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$width</span>=120;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$height</span>=40;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$img</span>=imagecreatetruecolor(<span class="variable">$width</span>,<span class="variable">$height</span>); //搭建验证码背景的宽高</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$element</span>=array(<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;d&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;e&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;f&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;g&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;h&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;i&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;j&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;k&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;m&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;p&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;q&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;s&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;t&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;v&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;y&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;z&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$string</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;//创建个空数组</span><br><span class="line">//ucwords(strtoupper(<span class="variable">$string</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>));//原本是想将string的内容强制装换成大写的，但是无法转换.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;4;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable">$string</span>.=<span class="variable">$element</span>[rand(0,count(<span class="variable">$element</span>)-1)];//随机从数组取值到空数组里</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorbg</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(150,255),rand(150,255),rand(150,255));//給验证码随机分配三原色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorBorder</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(200,255),rand(200,255),rand(200,255));//边框随机分配三原色 这部可以不需要只是添加函数用的</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$colorString</span>=imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(10,100),rand(10,100),rand(10,100));//线条随机分配三原色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">imagefill(<span class="variable">$img</span>,0,0,<span class="variable">$colorbg</span>);//创建验证码 参数风别是验证码，从x轴开始，从y轴开始，背景颜色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">imagerectangle(<span class="variable">$img</span>,0,0,<span class="variable">$width</span>-1,<span class="variable">$height</span>-1,<span class="variable">$colorBorder</span>);//创建边框 参数分别是验证码，从左x轴开始，从左y轴开始，从左x轴结束，从左y轴结束，背景颜色</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;100;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	imagesetpixel(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(0,<span class="variable">$width</span>-1),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>-1),imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(100,200),rand(100,200),rand(100,200)));//imagesetpixel是分配点，imagecolorallocate是点的颜色</span><br><span class="line">&#125;//循环給验证码添加小点,个人感觉这部完全没必要</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="variable">$i</span>=0;<span class="variable">$i</span>&lt;5;<span class="variable">$i</span>++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	imageline(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(0,<span class="variable">$width</span>/2),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>),rand(<span class="variable">$width</span>/2,<span class="variable">$width</span>),rand(0,<span class="variable">$height</span>),imagecolorallocate(<span class="variable">$img</span>,rand(100,200),rand(100,200),rand(100,200)));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;//循环給验证码画线  //创建边框 参数分别是验证码，从左x轴开始到中间结束，从左y轴开始到中间结束，从中间x轴到右边x轴结束，从中间y轴到右边y轴结束，背景颜色  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">imagettftext(<span class="variable">$img</span>,28,rand(-5,5),rand(15,20),rand(30,35),<span class="variable">$colorString</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;c:\WINDOWS\Fonts\STCAIYUN.TTF&#x27;</span>,<span class="variable">$string</span>);;//用Truetpye写入文本////imagestring(<span class="variable">$img</span>,5,0,0,<span class="string">&#x27;abcd&#x27;</span>,<span class="variable">$colorString</span>);//水平写入内容</span><br><span class="line">//imagettftext参数风别是验证码，字体大小，字体偏移角度，从x轴开始，从y轴开始，字体颜色,使用的字体路径，显示内容,</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">imagejpeg(<span class="variable">$img</span>);//告诉浏览器这是图片，头部一定要加header(<span class="string">&quot;Content-type:image/jpeg&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">imagedestroy(<span class="variable">$img</span>);//销毁图像回收资源不然会越运行越卡</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
